    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to works produced by the African people of the same name living in Burkina Faso, related to the Nunuma but living in an area to the south of them.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
